
README for dyndnsup


POST-INSTALLATION

    Copy the sample config file and edit to your needs:
    $ sudo cp /usr/etc/dydndnsup/dyndnsup.conf.sample \
      /usr/etc/dyndnsup/yourdomain.conf
    $ sudo $EDITOR /usr/etc/dyndnsup/yourdomain.conf

    Add a crontab line for doing auto-updates every 15 days:
    $ sudo crontab -e
    00 00 1/16 * * /usr/bin/dyndnsup -c /usr/etc/yourdomain.conf
